{"tid":718111,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"克羅地亞將出半力迎戰冰島","createTime":"2018-06-26T14:02:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-26T16:37:44.000Z","uid":19552,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"226194dc8dd3b8fdd84751aac62c3506b2dba841","tid":718111,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T14:02:11.000Z","msg":"由於克羅地亞已經打入16強，最後一場分組賽他們將會半力出擊，可能是冰島的搶分機會。<br />\n<br />\n冰島、尼日利亞及阿根廷將會爭奪D組最後一個出線名額，現時3支球隊都有機會晉級，隨時要鬥到最後才決定生死。<br />\n克羅地亞教頭戴歷表示，由於球隊已經晉級，所以他們將會半力出擊，收起莫迪歷、拿傑迪錫等一眾主力。戴歷說：「不理會其他對手的出線形勢及說話，我們只要專注做好自己。不要說甚麼派副選上陣，我們都是克羅地亞國家隊。」<br />\n冰島上場被尼日利亞打敗，更加暴露球隊不擅長進攻的特點，教練賀基姆臣指他們近4年來4次與克羅地亞交手，彼此非常熟悉，全隊將會力爭勝利擊敗對手。(<a href=\"http://Goal.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FGoal.com&d=jbrgomOfy58J3%2FUUrHu67MmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=581b811b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">Goal.com</a>)"},{"pid":"5ce1d07abebdc8420c3952f9fde3173b040dbf31","tid":718111,"uid":14965,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T14:06:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 蝗狗"},{"pid":"df214ab24fd32b81955d05be8fbff395e0335b3a","tid":718111,"uid":84013,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T14:10:47.000Z","msg":"收起莫迪歷、拿傑迪錫等一眾主力。<br />\n<br />\n死疤狗蝗狗都迫害美斯<br />\n<br />\n下季就轉會唔踢西甲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c9e0c0b5b4312bae3f5567875535eb5b2ff0a62","tid":718111,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T14:24:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ad1d48cc302389da479b29989ac11bef0db011b","tid":718111,"uid":18646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4c9e0c0b5b4312bae3f5567875535eb5b2ff0a62","tid":718111,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T14:24:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T14:31:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"422f2301e90d9713b210826eb53235a826a9e287","tid":718111,"uid":78971,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T14:34:52.000Z","msg":"戴歷說：「不理會其他對手的出線形勢及說話，我們只要專注做好自己。不要說甚麼派副選上陣，我們都是克羅地亞國家隊。」<br />\n<br />\n法國克羅地亞領隊講嘢好有大將之風"},{"pid":"2dc757533a85b5983bc435f6b82116fcc97ee769","tid":718111,"uid":22589,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T14:35:02.000Z","msg":"我地就唔用主力 吹咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"603bb4d7adce5d6f154eda60ce4e416a862bf8c9","tid":718111,"uid":180168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T14:36:30.000Z","msg":"畀其他球員踢下咪好<br />\n後備無得踢好慘"},{"pid":"133d0ecb01aa4b75d37449393f5b5d608e3f6cdc","tid":718111,"uid":6799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"603bb4d7adce5d6f154eda60ce4e416a862bf8c9","tid":718111,"uid":180168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T14:36:30.000Z","msg":"畀其他球員踢下咪好<br />\n後備無得踢好慘"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T14:37:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好人"},{"pid":"e146c845e6c1c25f8b3cac80bd8c1e1e27ab1a05","tid":718111,"uid":175402,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T14:38:57.000Z","msg":"其實好正常<br />\n出左線點解要同你博命<br />\n傷左仲唔抵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28bcfa980fb7116b045d995ec1dc28f5f10030a4","tid":718111,"uid":19552,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"422f2301e90d9713b210826eb53235a826a9e287","tid":718111,"uid":78971,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T14:34:52.000Z","msg":"戴歷說：「不理會其他對手的出線形勢及說話，我們只要專注做好自己。不要說甚麼派副選上陣，我們都是克羅地亞國家隊。」<br />\n<br />\n法國克羅地亞領隊講嘢好有大將之風"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T14:40:10.000Z","msg":"之前有條撚屌唔肯踢後備即刻比佢逐出隊"},{"pid":"c150e